
CKeditor in adva-cms
=====================

Simply do the following steps after adva install:

  rake adva:install plugins=adva_ckeditor    # Installs the adva_ckeditor plugin 
                                             # and symlinks assets 
Add Ckeditor.load! into your initializer.


For developers
==============

Add 'wysiwyg' to class of textarea:

  <%= f.text_area :my_textarea, :class => 'wysiwyg' %>

If you what to use small adva-cms toolbar then add "small" to your class as well:

  <%= f.text_area :my_textarea, :class => 'small wysiwyg' %>
